---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Experience">
  <div class="max-w-4xl bg-white p-6 md:p-10 rounded-lg shadow-md">
    <section class="mb-8">
      <div class="mb-4">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700">Software Engineer</h3>
        <p class="text-md text-gray-600">PalTech | June 2021 â€“ Present</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 italic">
          (Progressed through roles including Trainee, Associate, and Software
          Engineer levels)
        </p>
      </div>

      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        As an experienced Full Stack Developer, I have spent several years
        building and scaling robust web applications. My expertise spans both
        back-end and front-end development, API integration, database
        optimization, and cloud infrastructure management. I thrive in
        collaborative environments, contributing to product success, mentoring
        team members, and upholding code quality through best practices.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">
        Key Achievements & Responsibilities
      </h3>
      <ul
        class="list-disc list-outside space-y-3 pl-5 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed"
      >
        <li>
          <strong>Enhanced Application Security & Performance:</strong> Architected
          and implemented solutions that significantly reduced bot traffic, bolstering
          platform security. Led initiatives to optimize system performance, drastically
          improving query response times and reducing server load.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Improved User Experience & Efficiency:</strong> Spearheaded UI/UX
          improvements and resolved critical bugs, leading to measurable increases
          in user satisfaction. Introduced automation workflows that substantially
          improved team efficiency and reduced manual data entry time in key business
          processes.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Developed Scalable Systems & Features:</strong> Engineered complex
          features including automated financial reconciliation systems, enterprise
          authentication mechanisms (like OIDC and SSO), and advanced search functionalities.
          Architected and deployed applications on cloud platforms (AWS), establishing
          robust CI/CD pipelines for seamless delivery.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Billing & E-commerce Solutions:</strong> Designed, developed, and
          integrated comprehensive billing modules supporting multiple currencies
          and payment gateways (like Stripe ACH). Created custom billing flows for
          major app stores (like Shopify), contributing significantly to revenue
          growth and improving the customer checkout experience. Successfully managed
          complex database migrations and merges with zero data loss.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Technical Leadership & Mentorship:</strong> Provided technical
          mentorship to junior developers and played a key role in architectural
          decision-making to enhance system scalability, reliability, and maintainability.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">
        Technologies & Skills
      </h3>

      <div class="mb-4">
        <h4 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">
          Languages & Frameworks:
        </h4>
        <div>
          <span class="skill-tag">Ruby on Rails</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">JavaScript</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">TypeScript</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">ReactJS</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">NextJS</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Angular</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">NodeJS</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">NestJS</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-4">
        <h4 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Front-end:</h4>
        <div>
          <span class="skill-tag">HTML5</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">CSS3</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">TailwindCSS</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">StimulusJS</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Turbo</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-4">
        <h4 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Databases:</h4>
        <div>
          <span class="skill-tag">PostgreSQL</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">MongoDB</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">AWS RDS</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-4">
        <h4 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Cloud & DevOps:</h4>
        <div>
          <span class="skill-tag">AWS (EC2, S3, RDS)</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">CI/CD</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Git</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-4">
        <h4 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">
          APIs & Integrations:
        </h4>
        <div>
          <span class="skill-tag">REST APIs</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">GraphQL</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Stripe</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Shopify Apps</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">OAuth/OIDC</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Other:</h4>
        <div>
          <span class="skill-tag">System Architecture</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Database Migration & Optimization</span>
          <span class="skill-tag">Performance Tuning</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
<style>
  /* Style for skill tags */
  .skill-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: #e0f2fe; /* Light blue background */
    color: #0c4a6e; /* Darker blue text */
    font-size: 0.875rem; /* text-sm */
    font-weight: 500; /* font-medium */
    margin-right: 0.5rem; /* mr-2 */
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem; /* mb-2 */
    padding: 0.25rem 0.625rem; /* px-2.5 py-1 */
    border-radius: 0.375rem; /* rounded-md */
  }
</style>
